    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Complexes of buildings comprising the permanent establishment of a Christian missionary post or station. Buildings may include the central church, structures for the housing of the friars or other personnell, kitchen, storage, barns, surrounding grounds, and possibly other buildings.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
